  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Chop&nbsp;the <strong>bacon</strong> finely&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Heat a large, dry pan&nbsp;with a lid&nbsp;over a medium heat&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>bacon</strong> and cook for 3-5 min until crispy&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 700ml<span class=\"text-danger\">&nbsp;[1.4L]</span>&nbsp;<strong>boiled water</strong> to the bacon and crumble in the <strong>stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Whisk to dissolve the <strong>stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>&nbsp;and bring to the boil</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>cherry</strong></span><strong><span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span>tomatoes</strong> in half</p>\r\n<p>Grate the <strong>cheddar</strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel and slice the<strong> onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>&nbsp;finely</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the stock is boiling, reduce the heat to medium and add the <strong>linguine</strong> (break the linguine in half if it doesn't fit)</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>tomatoes</strong>, <strong>onion</strong>, <strong>garlic</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and half the grated<strong> cheddar</strong> to the pan</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>olive oil</strong>, 1 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\">&nbsp;[2 tsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>sugar</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong>&nbsp;pepper</strong> to the pot</p>\r\n<p>Cover with a lid&nbsp;and cook for 5 min</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 5 min, remove the lid, and stir continuously until the pasta is cooked and a sauce has formed (add more water if it looks too dry)</p>\r\n<p>Tip: stirring the sauce releases the starch from the pasta making it naturally creamier</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/317_step-6-x400.jpg",
